snippet.textDisplay:
For those that are bickering back and forth whether she sang Ave Maria in Italian or Latin...

Ave Maria is the Latin name of the prayer of Hail Mary.

HOWEVER...Christina sang the very heartfelt version of Franz Schubert's classic Ave Maria, all in Italian!!!

When Kobe was young he played basketball in Italy. He grew up in Italy & spoke fluent Italian.

If you don’t think she sang it in Italian, do your research and look it up. Every article states this!

This performance was amazing...so warm, angelic, beautifully done with so much grace and love! Thank you Christina!!! 🌹🌹🌹
